# Quiz Game 🎓

A command-line quiz game that asks the user a series of multiple-choice questions and displays a final score.

## Features
- 10 pre-defined questions
- Score calculation
- Immediate feedback after each question

## Technologies
- Python

## What I learned
- Structuring quiz logic
- Working with lists and conditions

## Run the game
```bash
python quiz.py
